data.message: Comprehensive review of all designs on Pencil board (50+ designs across Foundations drills, Lore CRM iterations, real project mockups, landing pages, and new designs): Scored and critiqued all major design sections. Identified patterns: dark theme comfort zone, strong functional UX, inconsistent visual delight. Top designs: Malawi Birthday Postcard (9/10), Seto-Rota Planner (8.5/10), Lore CRM V6 (8.5/10). Logged 6 learnings for compounding.
